2. Ensuring fair and efficient markets;

3. Providing efficient registration services.

As an onsite Talent Manager, my role is to provide end-to-end recruitment for a broad remit of stakeholders including Internal Audit & Operational Risk, Chief Legal Officer, Corporate Affairs, Financial Advisors and Markets. On a daily basis I recruit nationally for a broad range of positions, working with stakeholders to identify their needs and source high calibre talent to the business, develop effective sourcing strategies to engage candidates, pipeline candidates, create talent pools and conduct behavioural based panel interviews.

Responsible for:

